QuestData.Title: Report to Anselm
QuestData.Description: Let's send word back to old Anselm then. Victory has come later than expected, but better late than never. Tell him it will take our forces a few hours at most to finish off the stragglers here.$B$BGlory to the Banshee Queen!
QuestData.LogDescription: Report back to High Executor Anselm at Vengeance Landing in Howling Fjord.
QuestData.RewardText: It was about time. The Alliance has been a thorn in our side for a long time now.$B$BThere's no time to celebrate, however. Look to the west, it appears we have visitors.
